metadata.title: Funmunchkins First Birthday Outfit Girl, 1st Birthday Girl Outfit, Girl First Birthday Outfit
features: Made in the USA and Imported
description: Celebrate your little stars birthday with this personalized birthday outfit in pink and gold. Great for Twinkle Twinkle Little Start Theme Birthday Party or Princess Birthday Personalize with your child's name - NO EXTRA COST. Customized with the name of your little one. - FREE Please mention the name of the child in the notes section when placing the order. Cute Clean Design with a Royal Touch and Super Soft !! Great gifting idea !! Ideal for birthday photo shoots. If you need any other design or text please let me know and I can make it happen. I use high quality Carters bodysuit. Please mention your choice of bodysuit when placing the order. You can buy either the top only or the top/tutu or all 3 - top, tutu and headband. Fast Shipping. Excellent Customer Service.
